## Maritime Tracking — AIS

| Tool | Description | Free | Origin |
|------|-------------|------|--------|
| [MarineTraffic](https://www.marinetraffic.com) | Real-time AIS vessel tracking worldwide | 🔶 Freemium | 🇬🇷 Greece |
| [VesselFinder](https://www.vesselfinder.com) | Live vessel positions & port calls via AIS | 🔶 Freemium | 🇧🇬 Bulgaria |
| [ShipFinder](https://shipfinder.co) | AIS vessel tracking & port activity | 🔶 Freemium | 🇬🇧 UK |
| [Global Fishing Watch](https://globalfishingwatch.org) | Fishing vessel activity monitoring via AIS & satellite | ✅ | 🇺🇸 USA |
